lol_descInfo: Gets information about the module "League of Legends".
lol_descElo: Gets ranking information from a player. (?lol-elo SUMMONERNAME [SERVER=euw])
lol_descMatch: Gets information about a current match. (?lol-match SUMMONERNAME [SERVER=euw])
lol_descVersion: Gets the current version of the game.
lol_info: The module "League of Legends" adds additional commands for the same-named game.
